{"tid":262794,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★科通400 周三復牌!","createTime":"2017-05-29T13:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T07:59:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d414ecc41e7a1777625e808737254fb03a816512","tid":262794,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:23:29.000Z","msg":"29/5/2017 20:56<br />\n        科通芯城(00400)澄清沽空機構烽火研究的指控, 並指, 有關指控存在偏見、欺詐及誤導, 公司已向深圳警方報案, 保留採取法律行動的權利.<br />\n        烽火研究在上星期一發表報告, 質疑科通芯城誇大盈利, 形容是橫跨十年的「世紀騙案」. 報告指, 取得公司的工商檔案資料, 發現與公司披露的情況, 存在重大差異. 公司澄清, 報告所列工商檔案的收入, 只佔總收入的極少數, 大部分交易在香港進行, 入賬為香港產生的收入. 公司在內地有11間營運附屬公司, 而報告只引用6間公司的工商檔案.<br />\n        科通芯城否認報告所指, <a href=\"http://線上平台Cogobuy.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0Cogobuy.com&d=5kcKS88VDqQHtVy1SgIa4cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=386e1fed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">線上平台Cogobuy.com</a>未有更新, 又指, 股份回購符合上市規則的所有規定, 有關回購活動存在可疑之處的講法, 並無根據.<br />\n        科通芯城星期一股價大跌兩成二後中途停牌. 股份申請星期三復牌.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20170529205634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20170529205634&d=5kcKS88VDqQHtVy1SgIa4cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=9825c76a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20170529205634</a>"},{"pid":"a67d92a43f042a0b86dbe27c8acc5c2ce6616d4f","tid":262794,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:24:22.000Z","msg":"利好700<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad6d3e054f2f0980cc5c5c9feac639ee534c245","tid":262794,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\